TimeSeries¶

[22]:

from CactusTool import TimeSeries
from scipy.interpolate import interp1d
var = sim.Scalar.max['arena_mb'] # All scalar
table = var.dataset()
a = interp1d(table['time'], table['arena_mb'])
x = np.linspace(0, 60)

fig, ax = plt.subplots()
ax.plot(x, a(x))
plt.show()
